Class ShellScriptTask

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class ShellScriptTask
extends org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.ExecTask
    A generic front-end for passing "shell lines" to any application which can accept a filename containing script input (bash, perl, csh, tcsh, etc.). see antcontrib doc for usage
    Author:
    Stephan Beal, Peter Reilly
